cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Personascope"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Berczi
    given-names: Benjamin
  - family-names: Kim
    given-names: Kyuhee
repository-code: "https://github.com/benjibrcz/personascope"
abstract: >-
  A behavioural measurement pipeline for characterising how deeply LLMs adopt
  induced personas. Built on a three-stage pipeline
  (Preparation → Intervention → Measurement), it scores a model × persona ×
  induction-method configuration along Persona-Adoption Depth (PAD) and
  Value Drift (VD), with probes organized by functional category
  (identity, behavior, competence, cot, context_inference).
license: MIT
